text: Jonne is a Finnish variant of the given name John. Notable people with the name include: *Jonne Aaron (born 1983), Finnish singer *Jonne Hjelm (born 1988), Finnish footballer *Jonne Järvelä (born 1974), Finnish musician *Jonne Kemppinen (born 1981), Finnish footballer *Jonne Valtonen (born 1976), Finnish composer *Jonne Virtanen (born 1988), Finnish ice hockey player It is also the surname of Uruguayan footballer Luis Jonne. Category:Finnish masculine given names
